message.content:
a kitchen with dark gray cabinets and beige marble countertop, fridge to the right of the counter, 
counter has plates, red jam jars, a "CHICKY" chip packet, "JELLO" and "Alpen Salt" boxes, 
a dining table in the adjacent room with a bottle of water, a packet of biscuits, mugs and a wine glass, 
a rangehood above the stove, a sink on the counter, a pot on the stove and a white door with a silver handle.
